history.content:
Hey Guys,

Looking for a job or internship next year? 
Looking for FREE LUNCH?

If you said yes to either of these, then stop by the a16z Startup Career Fair and Demo Day tomorrow in the Soda Etcheverry breezeway from 11:30am to 1:30pm.

There will be 12 of Andreessen Horowitz's portfolio companies there looking to hire and show off their hot tech.

Check out the event page for more details

https://www.facebook.com/events/1590359517931976/
